Package: pkgsite
Title: Convert the reference pages into Quarto files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
  person("Edgar", "Ruiz", , "edgar@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person(given = "Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The goal of `pkgsite` is to make it easier to create a package 
  website using Quarto. It attempts to do for R what 'Quartodoc' does for Python 
  package documentation. 
